sentences: Jules Timothy Weisberg (born January 1, 1943) is an American flutist, vocalist, and record producer.
He had a hit song, "The Power of Gold", on Twin Sons of Different Mothers (1978), an album recorded with Dan Fogelberg.
He appeared on the TV show, The Midnight Special, hosted by Bobby Womack (Season 2, Episode 42), on July 12, 1974.
